<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Skyboard Game Invitation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #aaa;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Game Invitation</h2>
        </div>
        
        <p>Hi {{username}},</p>
        <p>{{inviter}} has entered invited you to join a lobby on Skyboard Games, with the lobby code <strong>{{lobbyCode}}</strong> and is waiting for you. Please head over to Skyboard to play.</p>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2024 Skyboard Games. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
